from the most basic to the most advanced,

64
00:02:18,272 --> 00:02:20,160
can help the teacher to describe

65
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,105
(what happened?),

66
00:02:21,105 --> 00:02:23,632
diagnose (why did it happen?),

67
00:02:23,632 --> 00:02:26,256
predict (what will happen?)

